# Changelog

## [0.1.1]
### Fixed
- (FormSubmitDirective): add the afterSubmit output

## [0.1.0]
### Added
- ParentControlContainerDirective

## [0.0.24]
### Fixed
- (FormDirective): cleanup submit and load process

## [0.0.23]
### Fixed
- (FormDirective): expose the current form definition

## [0.0.22]
### Fixed
- (RxapFormBuilder): use the definition constructor if not provided

## [0.0.21]
### Fixed
- (FormDirective): cdr change to public

## [0.0.20]
### Fixed
- (RxapFormBuilder): the builder state is overwritten by the option state

## [0.0.19]
### Fixed
- form directive typings

## [0.0.18]
### Added
- add exportAs to FormControlNameDirective and FormGroupNameDirective

## [0.0.17]
### Added
- FormControlNameDirective
- FormGroupNameDirective

## [0.0.16]
### Fixed
- (FormDirective): add missing error logs

## [0.0.15]
### Added
- FormType

## [0.0.14]
### Changed
- determine if a form submit fail only if an exception is thrown

## [0.0.13]
### Added
- add rxapOnInit support for form definitions

## [0.0.12]
### Changed
- add missing peer dependencies

## [0.0.11]
### Added
- FormSubmitDirective

## [0.0.10]
### Added
- ng-update support

## [0.0.9]
### Added
- RXAP_FORM_INITIAL_STATE Token
- ToFormSubmitMethod Method
### Changed
- log errors if load or submit fail

## [0.0.8]
### Fixed
- fix FormBuilder instance issue

## [0.0.7]
### Changed
- add optional controlId property
### Fixed
- form definition access from sub form groups
- change options type AbstractControlOptions to RxapAbstractControlOptions

## [0.0.6]
### Changed
- add support for @rxap/form-system

## [0.0.5]
### Added
- FormControlErrorDirective
- FormControlMarkDirtyDirective
- FormControlMarkPristineDirective
- FormControlMarkTouchedDirective
- FormControlMarkUntouchedDirective

## [0.0.4]
### Added
- @ControlSetValue

## [0.0.3]
### Changed
- update peer dependencies
- add @rxap/definition support

## [0.0.2]
### Added
